{"tid":359973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何俊仁：暫不判斷林子健有否誤導警務人員","createTime":"2017-08-15T01:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T02:59:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6aedb463d099969612407dd20f4a56fba8a9f6a","tid":359973,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】報稱被擄走的民主黨成員林子健因涉嫌誤導警務人員，凌晨在大角咀被捕。有份陪同林子健出席記者會的民主黨前主席何俊仁指，暫時不會判斷林子健有否誤導警務人員，而片段亦存有疑問，外界不應一口咬定戴口罩的男子就是林子健。<br />\n<br />\n被問到若事件屬實，民主黨是否需要道歉，他表示不想作這個假設。"},{"pid":"12785a5491575e01acf3a6d4138e44c8564e336f","tid":359973,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"民主黨向中共道歉我擔心會開心死成堆廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce600d1f574fab4fccdfc56ba1865dd67a3ea610","tid":359973,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:57:16.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾！"},{"pid":"cba0afd5f2e1015e4bc42df05c152e87f92edaf1","tid":359973,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨向中共道歉我擔心會開心死成堆廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n民主黨切腹都唔掂<br />\n<br />\n獨派滅民主黨係好難<br />\n估唔到民主黨會選擇自滅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86db87d9ad76ad44e99de4bf36c51f99ffaaa741","tid":359973,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T02:18:59.000Z